{"tid":833844,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真係睇唔透","createTime":"2018-09-23T19:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T08:37:29.000Z","uid":145395,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bd5c705ddc93f579c2dbfd735bdeb3e62cd1d3d5","tid":833844,"uid":145395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T19:50:56.000Z","msg":"每次收工行去搭車(1個星期三至四日啦)<br />\n經過新之城都會見到有對mk仔女坐向7仔or機鋪出面個梯級位<br />\n條女仲要抱住個b得幾個月大<br />\n條仔仲要好自豪咁擔住枝煙望住啲路人<br />\n有時仲有其他好兄弟姊妹客串<br />\n企左向到唔知做嘜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實個b好慘成日夜晚冇得舒服訓<br />\n向條街呼吸埋啲廢氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係笑鳩佢地都覺得自己折墮好似笑啲智商有問題既人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實有冇人見過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e741b0ebb9e3e25292b91eb133cf99026d662208","tid":833844,"uid":145395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T19:54:33.000Z","msg":"To bb仔 :下世唔好游咁快"},{"pid":"14a508899c110378babe9c8df711ac578f020997","tid":833844,"uid":129340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e741b0ebb9e3e25292b91eb133cf99026d662208","tid":833844,"uid":145395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T19:54:33.000Z","msg":"To bb仔 :下世唔好游咁快"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T20:54:09.000Z","msg":"出生咁既家庭都唔知係前世做錯咩事定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf73f332757e121b9bbf70ba37709effc0d89fb5","tid":833844,"uid":145395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14a508899c110378babe9c8df711ac578f020997","tid":833844,"uid":129340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e741b0ebb9e3e25292b91eb133cf99026d662208","tid":833844,"uid":145395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T19:54:33.000Z","msg":"To bb仔 :下世唔好游咁快"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T20:54:09.000Z","msg":"出生咁既家庭都唔知係前世做錯咩事定點<img src=\"/assets/fac